    "Through analysis, it is found that the models used in the experiment are based on Swan Transformer.",
    "In the calculation process, the amount of calculation in the second part (calculate the Attention Matrix and the value part) is mainly square with the number of partitioning modules M. This part cannot be reduced, which results in the reduction of parameters in the experiment being less than the theoretical value.",
